# WhatsApp Commerce App — Full Flow Documentation

## Overview

A full-stack WhatsApp Commerce order management system. Customers place orders via WhatsApp, receive Easypaisa payment links, and get automated status updates. Admins manage orders, products, and payments through a React dashboard.

**Stack:** TypeScript, Express.js, MongoDB (Mongoose), React (Vite), WhatsApp Cloud API, Easypaisa Payment Gateway.
**Deployment:** Vercel (serverless) or standalone Node.js server.

